SendMail. Sample usage of my CrtSock unit to send mails
(support HTML and Attached files).
SendMail is a console application with some parameters:
Host, From, To... (see readme.txt)
 
 
This little program can send a mail from command line or from a text file

1- SENDMAIL Host:smtp.server.com From:email To:email Cc:email Subject:"subject" body $include joinfile.ext body...
2- SENDMAIL FILE.TXT

FILE.TXT:
----------------------
Host:smtp.server.com
From:email
To:email
Cc:email
Subject:...subject...
...message...
$include joinfile.ext
....
